ولاية غرب إفريقية.صور: جنود الخلافة يقصفون معسكرا للجيش النيجيري المرتد في بلدة (ولغو) بمنطقة (برنو) بقذائف الهاون

ولاية غرب إفريقية.بتوفيق الله تعالى، كمن جنود الخلافة لدورية للجيش النيجيري المرتد، قرب بلدة (ولغو) بمنطقة (برنو)، واستهدفوها بمختلف أنواع الأسلحة، ما أدى لمقتل 3 عناصر وإصابة آخرين، واغتنم المجاهدون آلية رباعية الدفع وأسلحة وذخائر متنوعة، ولله الحمد.

ولاية غرب إفريقية.بتوفيق الله تعالى، استهدفت مفارز الإسناد لجنود الخلافة معسكرا وموقعا للجيش النيجيري المرتد، في بلدة (ولغو) بمنطقة (برنو)، بعشر قذائف هاون، ما أسفر عن مقتل وإصابة 7 عناصر، ولله الحمد.

ولاية غرب إفريقية.بتوفيق الله تعالى، فجّر جنود الخلافة عبوة ناسفة على رتل آليات للجيش النيجيري المرتد، على الطريق الرابط بين (مايدوغوري) و(دامبوا) بمنطقة (برنو) أول أمس، ما أدى لتدمير آلية رباعية الدفع ومقتل وإصابة من كان على متنها، ولله الحمد.

ولاية غرب إفريقية.بتوفيق الله تعالى، اشتبك جنود الخلافة مع رتل للجيش النيجيري المرتد، في بلدة (كوبوا) بين (دامبوا) و(سابون غاري) بمنطقة (برنو) أول أمس، بمختلف أنواع الأسلحة، ما أدى لتضرر بعض آلياتهم، ولله الحمد.
ولاية العراق - الأنبار.صور: بقايا عربة (همر) للجيش الرافضي المرتد في صحراء (راوة) دُمّرت بتفجير لجنود الخلافة

text: part 5..projection for btc/usdt in 2022: well that was a lot of talk with the point being that technical analysis is going into 2022 with a real disadvantage as there are far too many external factors that are going to exert an impact on bitcoin in 2022.  but i will give it a try anyway. ..based on performance over the past three years i calculated that with a start value of $46383 on 01 jan 2022 then btc/usdt has a high probability of reaching a value of at least $94.9k some time during the year of 2022.  ..if there is as much corporate investment support as there has been in 2021 then btc/usdt has the potential to rise up to $129.3k at some time during the year of 2022.  ..after reaching a peak value (some where between $94.9k and $129.3k) btc/usdt has a high probability of dropping in value down to $60.6k.    ..in summary my projection for btc/usdt is that it will be at or around $77771 usd at the end of the year on 31 dec 2022.

text: part 4..- investors and traders are waiting anxiously for a seamless means of paying for products and services using their cryptocurrency holdings via some form of ‘universal payment channel’ that visa and other credit card services are still working on (and have been since 2018).  this could happen in 2022 and when it does there will likely be a significant jump in bitcoin value.   .https://arxiv.org/ftp/arxiv/papers/2109/2109.12194.pdf ..- unfortunately as bitcoin rises in value the percentage of profit from daily oscillations gets smaller and smaller.  daily traders will end up moving away from bitcoin for daily trades but will expand into more forex-type trading and increase activity in ethereum and other popular cryptocurrencies. ..- also unfortunate as long as elon musk is alive and posting on social media dogecoin will continue to be a topic of discussion.  ..- and yet still more unfortunate due to the increasing acceptance of bitcoin combined with no true law enforcement opposition to the anonymity of fraudsters exit scammers and unethical investment operations plus the naivety and lack of knowledge among ‘new investors’ bitcoin will still be hit by negative news media regarding ‘cryptocurrency fraud’ even when the fraud in question does not actually involve cryptocurrencies.

column1: 1563_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2022-01-02
text: part 3..- as a counter to the loss of china the leading economic countries around the world have grudgingly accepted bitcoin as a valid means of transaction including most of the european union the united kingdom the big three in north america (canada mexico and usa) australia and japan with el salvador being the first to adopt bitcoin as a legal tender.  other than china the other 41 countries worldwide who have absolute bans on cryptocurrency transactions had no significant impact on the value of bitcoin in the past and aren’t likely to in the future.   .https://www.investopedia.com/articles/forex/041515/countries-where-bitcoin-legal-illegal.asp .  .- regarding corporate leaders executives and their trading representatives most have been away on holiday vacation since 15 dec 2021 after getting their fourth quarter bonuses and will become active again starting 04 jan 2022; we should start seeing them playing their games again by 14 jan 2021 at the latest.  regarding media sources some sources are predicting a slump in value in the new year but most sources are currently supporting an optimistic viewpoint in turn supported by the boom in nfts which is still ongoing. imo if anything is going to have a negative effect on bitcoin in 2022 it is going to be the nft bubble as there is a lot of copyrighted content being fraudulently acquired and traded.     .https://www.barrons.com/articles/bitcoin-prices-crypto-outlook-2022-51640718532   .https://www.artnews.com/art-news/news/nft-market-research-1234612143/

column1: 1529_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-12-06
text: bitcoin btc/usdt:  as much as i would love to be correct for my end of year projection reality must take precedent. ..the trend line that was put into place on 20 oct 2021 (the transparent orange triangle on the chart based on the pattern from the downward trend after the apr 2021 peak) indicates a continued downward trend down to $32.7k by 26 jan 2021.  however this was based on bitcoin pattern 3 which i assess is no longer valid.  we also have to bear in mind the following considerations. ..point a) there are some organizations that want btc/usdt to get back above $60k as soon as possible.  case in point is micro strategy which made far too many purchases (over 7000) of btc/usdt at an average value of $59k (a prime suspect for my ‘corporate interference’ accusations).   ..point b) based on the current change in trend from the low of $42.1k back up to the current $49.4k (and supported by news sources) it appears unlikely that btc/usdt will drop below $40k again over the next month.  there are far too many nations and organizations waiting to buy up ‘cheap’ bitcoin as soon as it gets that low.

column1: 1528_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-12-06
text: so how high will it go now? netadvisor published a listing of predictions (as did many other websites) with so-called cryptocurrency experts calling for up to $100k by the end of 2021.  unfortunately cryptocurrencies are not rockets with a constant release of fuel that causes them to go ever-and-ever faster (or in this case higher and higher in value).  they are part of oscillating cycles that go up and down as they have ever since they started operating and if you don’t build oscillations into your forecast then you are just schilling and hyping a category that i think most of these ‘experts’ fall into.   my conservative projection from 01 jan 2021 was for a value for btc/usdt of $48623 by end 31 dec 2021 and if it ends up off by up to 10% either way (a range of $43.7k to $53.4k) i will still call it a hell of a lot better than most of the projections i’ve seen published this year.  based on a current value of $49461 and only 26 days to the end of the year i still have a good chance of being correct.

column1: 1527_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-12-06
text: 🌎 summary of altcoin activity 🌎..__updated as of 05 dec 2021 (2200 utc) (#35) by @ultracrepidarianx.for coincidental trading the telegram trading channel with a community feeling. ..__general update: finally after almost three weeks what i refer to as ‘interference’ has finally ended on 03 dec 2021 and bitcoin was finally allowed to drop in value like i projected it was supposed to.  over the last two days a variety of crypto news sources have stated reasons for the ‘shocking’ drop in value most of them citing external causes related to politics environment or the stock market.  to me the cause is very simple; the corporate entity that was buying into bitcoin every time it dropped down to or below the 55k line finally (a) ran out of resources for propping up the value or (b) achieved their monetary goals possibly selling off some assets for a pretty profit.   ..once the drop started to hit stop/loss settings it was just a case of seeing how far it would drop before it settled again with the smart investors buying in at the bottom (i.e. el salvador bought another 100 btc on 26 nov 2021 now holding over 800 btc).  surprisingly some companies like microstrategy announced recent purchases of 7000 btc at an average price of just over $59k each for a total of over 121000 btc in holdings at an average of $29k per coin.  based on these types of reports corporate investors and national government are banking on the value of btc/usdt to increase in value over the coming year and over the next five years.

text: ethereum eth/btc:  while we watch the btc activity we cant forget to see the effects on ethereum.  the previous assessment projected a rise in ethereum based on a drop in bitcoin.  lacking the drop in bitcoin plus a subsequent resurgence in btc it is no surprise that ethereum has faltered since 08 nov 2021.  the rise in eth/btc value on 10 and 11 nov 2021 is a match for the drops in btc/usdt values on the same dates.  while btc/usdt floats in the $63 to 65k bracket ethereum is expected to stay within the 70000 to 74000 bracket.  if btc/usdt rises over $65k in the next five days expect a drop in eth/btc down to 70000 or lower down to 69000 if eth/btc is already at 70000.

column1: 1499_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-11-15
text: the affect on daily traders is simple.  the likelihood of good trades on btc of greater than 5% over a 48 hour period are gone for the near future making this an undesirable coin for daily trades.  with a good bot running you could still take advantage of the slight increases and decreases.  for the long term it looks like a very high probability of the value of bitcoin rising again over the coming month.  if this trend of corporate interference continues it is possible that the value will increase to over $80k by the end of the year but needs to be monitored for sustainability.

column1: 1498_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-11-15
text: who buys btc at $60k when all past indicators have shown the value is likely to drop by as much as 50% after hitting a peak? who buys btc at $63k when the chance of profit is less than 5% unless the coin is going up past a previous high established just a week earlier?   certainly not any trader i know of.  the only answer i see is a corporate entity who has a plan for keeping the value of btc/usdt above $60k.  since 25 oct there have been at least 16 pushes that resulted in btc/usdt staying above $60k and eventually up to a new record of just over $69k.  in summary an unidentified corporate or grouping of corporates has identified how to keep btc/usdt value stable and above $60k protecting their investments and providing a base line for a continued increase in value.  however maintaining a stable coin value requires a constant influx of investment and it is uncertain how long the organizer of this stability can keep up the investment.  it is likely that the investments are coordinated with shorts and longs that take advantage of knowing when the next investment will occur to push the value back up again.  it is unlikely that any group of traders or even whales can counter this corporate interference.  unfortunately i don’t know how they are doing it or how the use of stablecoins makes this possible but it appears to be working at this time.  but i can recognize interference in established patterns and i see interference going on here.  how rich do you need to be to do this?  i am thinking this would require a slush fund of about $10 billion

column1: 1497_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-11-15
text: part a4 – the empire strikes back) this fourth phase that i see is not supported by any current articles; but at least one article posted by nasdaq.com on 13 nov 2021 does a pretty good job of explaining the influence of how corporate investors have switched from volatile bitcoin -based investments to stablecoin investments which is reputed to be part of the current btc/usdt stability.  for my part ever since the value dropped into the $60-65k bracket on 21 oct i have been seeing signs of unusual purchases that do not match previous patterns of activity for btc/usdt in previous years; they don’t even match previous patterns of trader or whale buy/sell activity.  the most significant result being that the coin keeps getting pumped up by purchases whenever it tries to drop below %60k.  i refer to this pattern of activity as ‘corporate interference’. .https://www.nasdaq.com/articles/why-did-the-bitcoin-price-dip-from-all-time-highs-2021-11-13

column1: 1496_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-11-15
text: part a3 – the phantom menace) the third phase is the rise of the cryptocurrency influencer (‘crypto-jedi’?) running from feb 2021 to oct 2021.  with tesla revealing their purchases of $1.5 billion worth of cryptocurrencies (on 02 feb 2021) and elon musk advocating cryptocurrency as a valid investment the negative news articles posted about the dangers of cryptocurrencies disappear; if elon musk supports it it must be great!  (there are many other influencers or events that could be cited as causes for increased popularity but this is my assessment of the most influential).  however the cryptocurrencies remain just as volatile; traders and whales buy and sell based on reactions from the postings of influencers creating self-fulfilling prophesies (and values).  the increased positive reviews of cryptocurrency investments leads to even greater acceptance of cryptocurrencies as a valid investment and a means of purchasing items like vehicles and houses.  however even the influencers are erratic with great swings in value based on whether their comments are negative or positive.  the value of btc/usdt rises on 20 oct 2021 to a new high of just over $66000.

column1: 1495_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-11-15
text: part a2 – a new hope) the second phase ran from october 2020 to jan 2021.  amid reports of increased corporate interest as early as jan 2020 the reports in oct 2020 of square inc buying 4709 bitcoins for a total price of $50 million (averaging $10.6k each) was just the tip of the iceberg.  hundreds of credible corporations in north america europe and asia began covertly investing in cryptocurrencies.  as the value of btc/usdt rose past $34k at the end of jan 2021 the value was still being affected by whale-level buys and sells but caution was setting in.  instead of whales pushing values up it was likely that most of this increase was due to corporate purchases being held for long-term investment.  in turn massive fomo set in as no one wanted to sell their btc/usdt at $34k only to see it rise higher.  in addition the value was extremely erratic and volatile with the value of btc/usdt rising and falling by as much as $10k over a 48 hour period; any large sell-off sent the value crashing dramatically and any large purchase causes a massive skyrocket upwards.  an excellent era for daily traders and ‘leveragers’ who have made the right call.  of note coordinated groups that i think of as mmot (massive multiplayer online traders) were still able to take on corporate giants (i.e. redditors vs wall street hedge funds).https://squareup.com/us/en/press/2020-bitcoin-investment

column1: 1429_Coincidental Trading (Free Signals - for Binance, KuCoin & more)_2021-10-24
text: in my opinion the etf has had much less impact than expected and a lot of corporates who set up longs on btc/usdt last week are keeping the coin above $60k to keep their longs from failing.  i expect to see a small rise in value come monday morning but lacking any significant support i am expecting btc/usdt to drop over the next 72 hours. by how much is difficult to determine – how badly do corporate investors want to continue to support the coin above the $60k line?   ..support for this comes from past patterns in december 2017 (launch of futures contracts on the chicago exchange rise up to $19.8k) and in april 2021 (after debut of coinbase stock listing on nasdaq rose up to $63.4k).  each of these was preceded by heavy increase in btc value and followed by heavy drop in btc value.  at least one source (coindesk) supports this projection example provided below. .https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2021/10/19/analysts-divided-on-prospects-of-sell-the-fact-move-as-bitcoin-etf-listing-nears/

text: part b) why so slow of a drop?  a lot of what is happening is tied to the first bitcoin etf in the usa launched by proshares and approved by the american sec.  the peak value occurred at 20 oct 2021 1400 utc which is equal to 10 am in new york (eastern seaboard) and 7am in los angeles (western seaboard).  lacking any notable postings from musk or other influencers this implies that the us stock market was the biggest influencer during this time period assisted by excessive hype prior to 20 october that the etf was going to result in the value of btc/usdt rising up to 170% by the end of the year (yikers!).  examples provided below. .https://www.marketwatch.com/story/the-2-reasons-bitcoin-could-surge-by-170-to-168-000-by-year-end-as-crypto-linked-etfs-roll-out-11634584395 .https://finance.yahoo.com/news/new-bitcoin-etf-could-trigger-rally-to-168000-fundstrat-195756268.html

this is where vega can come into.play. (ex: holding puts through.earnings and the stock does go down.but not a huge amount you will more.than likely lose on the trade because.the iv will go back to normal and.vega will combine with that and.crush your gains).

📌 implied volatility:.the supply/demand % in which the.contracts are being traded at. higher.implied volatility means more people.are interested in trading those.contracts as there is usually a.catalyst behind it such as news or.earnings. regular implied volatility.sits around 50% and anything above.that means there is higher demand..be careful though trading options.with high implied volatility (over 90%).as they can have an "iv crush" which.is when the volatility goes back to.normal levels.
📌 volume:.this refers to the total contracts.traded in a given trading session..just like with any other stock higher.volume means better price action.and more liquid trades.

📌 open interest:.the total number of option contracts.that are currently out there. meaning.they have been traded but not yet.liquidated. this does not update.throughout the day. but usually the.higher the open interest the better.that contract selection looks to.investors as it shows larger holdings.at a specific price.
here are a few other key things to.keep in mind when looking for option.contracts:
like i said above there is really no.need to focus on gamma vega or.rho as most traders will go based off.delta and theta. but you now at least.have a reference to the greeks!
the rho is 0.07 meaning there will be.a change in the option value if.interest rates increase/decrease.
the vega is 0.20 meaning if the.implied volatility changes 1 point you.will see a $20 price movement up or.down depending on the direction of.the point change
the gamma is 0.02 meaning this will.move relatively slowly if aapl moves.$1.
the theta is -0.06 meaning everyday.this contract will lose $6 in value.

so each contract that you can.choose (this includes any and all.strike prices) will have different.greeks. going back to our 140 call for.aapl; lets say we chose to expire on.march 19th of 2022.
now this might get a bit heady and.confusing here. but no worries as.most options traders focus on delta.and theta. however i will still explain.how these all come to fruition.

a. __delta:__ the amount in which the.option premium is expected to move.on a $1 change in the underlying.stock value..b. __theta:__ theta is when contract.decay starts to happen as the time in.the day starts to diminish the.contract will lose premium..c. __gamma:__ the rate that delta will.change based on a $1 change in the.underlying stock price. aka the.speed at which the premium will.move with the delta..d. __vega:__ as the implied volatility.changes this is the amount the.option premium will change up or.down with time..e. __rho:__ this is the amount the.option premium will change based on.a percentage change in interest rate.
__the greeks__ __:__.mentioned above there are.components called "greeks" that play.a part in the prices and price action.of options. there are 5 different.greeks :
like it has been mentioned before.there are contracts out there for every.type of trader/investor! this leads us.into a very important category. the.greeks.

to prevent this decay from.happening some people choose.longer expirations to combat this..others will choose daily or weekly.contracts because there is more.volatility which = more price action to.day trade.

time value means that the longer the.contract has until expiration then the.less "time decay" it has. less time.decay means less volatility in.swinging a specific contract. since.everyday contracts will lose value in."time decay. the closer you get to.expiration the faster the time decay.takes over as seen on the chart.
a time value chart will be provided for.a visual example. when time is.involved this is where another greek.gets involved called theta.
since you have more time for the.underlying stock to move up or down.you will pay a higher premium as less.risk is associated with this type of.play.
no matter what expiration you.choose one thing can be certain the.further out you go in expiration the.more expensive the contract will be.

as discussed above different strikes.have different prices. the same.concept is applied for expirations..optionable stocks will have.expiration attached to the contract.that you can purchase. as mentioned.some will have weeklies all the way.to yearlys and others might just have.monthlies or biweeklies.
no matter what expiration selection.is important for any investor as you.must pick one to trade an option..however different expirations have.different prices attached to the strike.price.

for some the expiration is the most.important part as it gives solidified.dates for swing and longer-term.trades. whereas others buy and sell.in the same day and expiration just.plays into the price of the contract.

text: voting rights.vecrv holders can vote on how much crv emissions (yield) every pool gets this is called "gauge weight". the higher the gauge the more crv yield is going to lps in that particular pool. you can see why this is important as the higher the yield for lps in a pool the more liquidity it attracts...reward boosts.on top of that holding vecrv gives liquidity providers on curve a boost (up to 2.5x) of their yield on their pool. .this creates a loop where lps are incentivized to hold more vecrv to receive more crv. and the lockups of crv makes the token more illiquid and this creates a bullish alignment for all involved participants and keep the yield for aggregators and lps high. these tokenomics are very sophisticated...tldr.curve is the most important protocol for stablecoins as it has the deepest liquidity. this liquidity is ensured by the above outlined mechanisms. now why is liquidity so important especially for stablecoins?..because the deeper the liquidity the more secure is the peg of the stablecoin (!!!). this is the most important point here the reason for the so-called curve wars and the key-takeaway here. this is the reason why stablecoin protocols compete against each other over influence on gauge weights because the higher the gauge the more liquidity is in their pools and the more liquidity is in there pools the more stable is their peg..this is what its all about...in vol. 2 we will take a closer look at the participants of this fight there methods and why and how the voting power on curve can be monetized...for blockchain whispers family (exclusively!).mr. y - lead fundamental analyst

column1: 2951_Blockchain Whispers ® Official (By D Man) -- The Most Amazing Crypto Channel Ever Created By Mankind!_2022-02-06
text: the curve wars vol.1.in this two-part series we want to outline the whole curve universe and help you gain an understanding what is happening and why it is important...what is curve?.curve is an automated market maker (amm) exchange that is based on an improved model of the bonding curve and focused on trading similarly priced assets like stablecoins or different forms of wrapped btc (for example renbtc and wbtc). this design minimizes impermanent loss slippage and fees. because pools with similar assets are trending towards the same price it is unlikely that any token inside the pool will slide too far of peg. with much smaller fluctuations as opposed to a pool with heterogenic assets the trading fees are much smaller as on other amms (fees are used to compensate liquidity providers for impermanent loss so when we have reduced risk of impermant loss we can offer lower fees). and these smaller fees attract liquidity and the deeper the liquidity the lesser the slippage. a perfect circle:..reduced il -> reduced fees -> increasing liquidity -> smaller fees..on top of that comes an underlying functionality of curve that allows the assets into the pools to automatically get lent out to interest-paying platforms like compound aave and synthetix. this way curve can reward lps not only with trading fees and instead offer interest rates on top of that...the backbone of defi.the above described mechanisms make curve to the most capital efficient amm for swaps between homogenic assets and the yield for lps from the underlying lending mechanism to interest bearing protocols make curve a cornerstone for other yield-generating protocols like yearn and convex...this extremely efficient composability is paired with a very high degree of security. curves smart contracts are audited and non-upgradeable this means they cannot changed no matter what. this leaves users in full control of their funds and eliminates the possibility of a rug pull while also makes the protocol extremely difficult to hack. ..the combination of these features and mechanics make curve the protocol with the highest tvl (total value locked) overall. with a tvl of 19.2 billion usd and daily volumes between 400 and 500 million $ it has the deepest liquidity in stablecoin pools and it is the undisputed nr. 1 in defi. these unique properties are the reason that a huge chunk of defi yield (across different protocols and yield aggregators) is produced by curve which makes it essentially the foundation of defi.......the native token of curve is crv and it is an erc20 governance token with voting power (remember this as it will be important later).  ..__total supply: __.62% to community liquidity providers.30% to shareholders (team investors) with 2-4 years vesting.3% to employees with 2 years vesting.5% to the community reserve..holders of crv can lock their tokens to gain voting power. if a user locks crv tokens he receives vecrv tokens (ve stands for vote escrowed ) these tokens grant you voting power and a share of the trading fees. vecrv is non transferable and cannot be traded...now pay attention. the longer you lock your cvr the more vecrv you receive the maximum is 4 years. when you lock crv for 4 years you receive vecrv in a 1:1 ratio if you look it for 1 year your receive 0.25 vecrv per crv and so an. the longer you lock your tokens the more voting power and revenue share you get and your vecrv balance is decreasing over time unless you choose to lock more crv or extend the lock period. locking crv to get vecrv is irreversible. doing so has several benefits: .vecrv grants the user a share of the trading views voting rights in the curvedao and boosted crv rewards. .lets talk about each point...trading fees.every vecrv holder earns a portion of the protocols revenue (generated through swap fees). 50% of all trading fees are collected and used to buy 3crv (the lp token for the tripool which consists of dai usdc and usdt) which is then distributed to all holders. these lp tokens can be redeemed for the underlying collateral.

you all have to understand “the who the guy is behind the screen!”.i learned things from my grandmother almost 30 years ago that have stuck with me. she was the best! taught me so many life lessons up until i was 15 when she left this earth. .she was a “giver” in life. it was always about someone else. .when she passed away at 67 i never saw so many people at a wake before unless it was on tv. the people who came to pay their respects to her and our family were wrapped around two blocks! they were all there for our “grandma!” the stories i remembered hearing those two nights were unreal. how she would hear someone’s husband passed away and they had nothing. she would get a group of her friends to set the wife up and get assistance for her rent or bills so she could get on her feet! stories of a superhero not just a grandma! ..she passed away in october the 25th it’s exactly a month away and i always reflect on it when sept rolls around...that’s the imprint she left on this world!.this is what life is about!.life is way too short! help someone else! the reward is 10 fold!.simple things like to stop from rushing and looking at your phone when walking out of a store .wait the 10 seconds for the person behind you and hold the door open. watch the response from he/she when they get up to that door!..i say it all the time. karma is real!.you will get soo much more from life if you give back. ..telling you i have seen it with my own eyes. a 67 year old widow. that retired at 61 years old and two weeks later found a lump on her breast. she had cancer before ever getting a retirement check. but she didn’t let that cancer define her. she had surgery went through chemo and was told things weren’t looking good. they didn’t give her a year to live. this was the early 90’s. totally different than today. .not for one day did i ever see her feel sorry for herself. she kept up with her friends. she continued to assist in raising us along with her other 10 grand children. .this woman was a true warrior! .she battled and beat it. instead of not being here a year later. she thrived and beat the odds. all while giving amazing love to her family being with her friends and helping strangers. she opened a food bank and gave to soooo many families that didn’t know why this woman would be doing all of this!.why did she do it? that’s just who she was and what she was made up of. a person put on this earth to give and help others! others that she had mostly never met until they needed her or met her through someone else. .yes the cancer came back 5 years later it was much more aggressive. even though the second bout had taken her life it never defined her for a single day. .i miss that woman every single day! she was my second mom!.👆🏻.so for all the newer members of cw now you can understand “the why” i am here answering ?’s in dm from someone i have never spoken to. .it’s just who i am!..i want you all to reach your goal of financial freedom! 💪🏼💪🏼.let’s get it!

[​​](https://telegra.ph/file/ee505656ba285771c6c91.mp4)💠 продолжая тему nft хотел поделиться с вами одним очень недооценённым проектом который имеет все шансы на то чтобы обрести большую популярность в будущем...[pow nft](https://www.pownft.com/) - первый в мире nft добываемый с помощью майнинга. фишка в том что майнинг происходит в браузере и доступен абсолютно каждому - благодаря этому происходит справедливое распределение токенов...с каждым удвоением общего количества добытых атомов сложность их добычи увеличивается втрое что создаёт дефицит токенов. каждое удвоение называется поколением. например сейчас 11 поколение - последний добытый атом 3309...коллекция состоит из атомов входящих в периодическую систему менделеева - например hydrogen oxygen и так далее. всего может быть добыто в районе 17000 токенов благодаря бомбе сложности. каждый токен уникален и не повторяется благодаря индивидуальным свойствам - наличие ионов заряда цвет траектория движения атомов поколение.....когда вы добыли токен (нашли нужный хэш) вам даётся возможность приобрести его за 0.1 eth. но эти деньги идут не создателю токена а распределяются между держателями прошлых поколений! то есть эти токены генерируют доход. плюс с каждым поколением цена покупки атома возрастает вдвое...проект пока не очень популярен и токены добыть всё ещё достаточно легко. лично я добыл уже 2 атома. каждый из них можно продать уже минимум за 0.2 eth на opensea.io - то есть фактически я сделал х2. но я не стану их продавать как минимум несколько месяцев...внизу я прикреплю один из своих токенов имеющий редкое свойство - 2 отрицательно заряженных частицы...данный nft имеет всё необходимое для того чтобы выстрелить:..• оригинальность идеи - это первый проект совместивший майнинг и nft...• дефицит токенов. ..• добыча атома требует усилий и сложность добычи постоянно растёт что повышает ценность атомов...• стоимость добычи увеличивается вдвое с каждым поколением атомов...• каждый токен - уникален. в коллекции встречаются особо редкие атомы которые будут цениться больше чем остальные. и у любого человека есть шанс их добыть...итак для добычи вам понадобится установленный в браузере metamask.io и где-то $250 на кошельке в ethereum. ..стоимость добычи токена на данный момент - 0.1 eth. но для подтверждения добычи требуется газ. не жалейте его иначе вас могут опередить - все майнеры соревнуются между собой и кто-то может подтвердить добычу токена раньше вас. поэтому как только вам удалось найти хэш сразу подтверждайте транзакцию и выставляйте максимальное количество газа. комиссия будет в районе $50...для вас участие в данном проекте это возможность получить редкие nft на раннем этапе и шанс сделать хороший капитал затратив при этом немного. через несколько месяцев токены могут продаваться в десятки раз дороже чем сейчас...если вас заинтересовал проект я рекомендую изучить инструкцию по майнингу на сайте проекта...pownft.com

[​​](https://telegra.ph/file/73379cd44c06234628dec.jpg)💠 nft - non-fungible token или невзаимозаменяемый токен (erc-721)...что это такое? я бы мог написать целую статью с заумными терминами но это не передаст суть явления. на самом деле всё можно объяснить гораздо проще на примере нескольких аналогий...в реальном мире есть множество редких и уникальных предметов за которые коллекционеры готовы платить целые состояния - картины великих художников старые вина коллекционные монеты и даже марки. ..тоже самое есть и в виртуальном мире - например в steam есть торговая площадка на которой каждый день покупаются и продаются косметические предметы многие из которых стали коллекционными благодаря своей редкости. пользуются популярностью например шапки из team fortress скины на оружие в cs go и так далее... отдельные предметы продаются за десятки тысяч долларов...чем популярнее реже и уникальнее предмет - тем больше он ценится. и это относится не только к реальному миру но и к виртуальному. каждый человек будет получает удовольствие лишь от факта владения подобным предметом - ведь его больше нет ни у кого в мире или им обладает очень малое количество людей...но коллекционные предметы в реальном мире часто подделываются. плюс их можно испортить если неправильно обращаться с ними или хранить...у коллекционных предметов в виртуальном мире также есть минусы - например вы не являетесь их фактическим владельцем. все права принадлежат разработчику игры или владельцам площадки steam. в теории они в любой момент могут сделать с вашим имуществом всё что угодно и им за это ничего не будет. плюс они контролируют эмиссию - если разработчики захотят они выпустят на рынок большое количество предметов которые ранее были редкими...блокчеин способен решить данные проблемы на помощь приходит nft...в чём главная ценность блокчеина? в первую очередь ценность блокчеина в том что вы и только вы являетесь владельцами ваших активов. ни банк ни организация ни какой-то дядя... а именно вы. ..технология nft позволяет хранить уникальные предметы у себя на кошельке. ценность каждого отдельно взятого nft определяется рынком сообществом. а сообщество ценит редкие и уникальные свойства...например cryptopunks - один из самых первых nft-проектов. криптопанки - это 10000 уникальных карточек с пиксельным изображением различных персонажей в панк-стилистике. ..первое что поднимает ценность этого nft - данный проект один из первых nft если не самый первый. кстати по той же причине многие ценят биткоин - ведь он является первой криптовалютой. первенство - это всегда редкое и уникальное качество которое невозможно повторить...второе за что ценят криптопанков - каждый из них уникален среди 10000 панков не встречается одинаковых персонажей...пару дней назад один из криптопанков был продан за 7.5 млн $ несмотря на то что изначально их вообще раздавали бесплатно несколько лет назад...также многие из вас слышали про криптокотиков - это тоже nft. ..почти каждый день появляются новые nft-проекты. большинство из них мусор который никогда не будет цениться сообществом. но иногда встречаются очень интересные nft которые сочетают в себе отличную идею редкость и уникальность. я рекомендую вам следить за данным рынком. возможно вам удастся заполучить nft который в будущем будет цениться также как и криптопанки...полезные ссылки:..opensea.io - самая популярная торговая площадка на которой продаются и покупаются nft-токены. ..rarible.com - вторая по популярности площадка...cryptoslam.io - аналог coinmarketcap для мира nft. советую там искать новые ещё не успевшие обрести популярность проекты.
